9 Relating to recycling; to amend Section 22-27-12, Code
10 of Alabama 1975, to require the Alabama Department of
11 Environmental Management to adopt rules providing for the
12 beneficial reuse of foundry sand; and to make nonsubstantive,
13 technical revisions to update the existing code language to
14 current style..
